frame.name: Frame
frame.description: Frame used to change your profile background.

wood.name: Wood
wood.description: Log of wood cut by axe. To collect use the `wood` command!

wooden-plank.name: Wooden Plank
wooden-plank.description: Wooden Plank processed by a saw. To create this item use the command `saw`!

coal.name: Coal
coal.description: Piece of coal used to heat the furnace and forge metal bars. Bonus for mining some ores with the command `mine`!

copper-ore.name: Copper Ore
copper-ore.description: Mined copper ore that can be forged in a bar. To collect use the command `mine`!

copper-bar.name: Copper Bar
copper-bar.description: Copper bar forged with ore and a piece of coal. To create use the `forge` command!

iron-ore.name: Iron Ore
iron-ore.description: Mined iron ore that can be forged in a bar. To collect use the command `mine`!

fence.name: Wooden Fence

common_box.name: Common Box

uncommon_box.description: Uncommon box that will give you good rewards! Open it using the `box` command

basic_fertilizer.name: Basic Fertilizer
basic_fertilizer.description: A basic Fertilizer to help with your harvest, ensures an increase of 5% to 25%!

medium_fertilizer.name: Medium Fertilizer
medium_fertilizer.description: An average fertilizer that ensures a reasonable increase of 15% to 35% in your harvest!

premium_fertilizer.name: Premium Fertilizer
premium_fertilizer.description: The best of Fertilizers, ensures an increase of 25% to 50% in your harvest!

small_fishing-net.name: Small Fishing Net
small_fishing-net.description: A basic fishing net with small size, ensures an improvement of 5% to 10% in your fishing!

medium_fishing-net.name: Medium Fishing Net
medium_fishing-net.description: A reasonable fishing net ensures a 10% to 20% improvement in your fishing!

large_fishing-net.name: Large Fishing Net
large_fishing-net.description: The largest fishing net to catch fish, ensures an improvement of 15% to 30% in your fishing!

small_bomb.name: Small Bomb
small_bomb.description: A small explosive that opens small holes, will help you in your mining ensuring an increase of 5% to 10%!

medium_bomb.name: Medium Bomb
medium_bomb.description: A medium explosive that paves the way through the mine, ensuring an increase of 10% to 15% in your mining!

large_bomb.name: Large Bomb
large_bomb.description: A powerful explosive that will open up large spaces and ensuring a 15% to 25% increase in your mining!
